# Patch Workflow

This document describes how to generate, apply, and push patches in this repository using the provided helper scripts.

## 1. Reset and Clean (if needed)

```bash
git fetch origin main
git switch main
git reset --hard origin/main
git clean -fdx
```

## 2. Stage Your Changes

